        <Parent_String>Paleozoic [300391254], Phanerozoic [300391251], geologic time scale [300391250], styles, periods, and cultures by general era [300111078], Styles and Periods (hierarchy name) [300015646], Styles and Periods Facet [300264088]</Parent_String>
